original_sentence: 9.2.5.2 UE procedure for multiplexing HARQ-ACK/SR/CSI in a PUCCH  For a transmission occasion of a single CSI report, a PUCCH resource is provided by pucch-CSI-ResourceList. For a transmission occasion of multiple CSI reports, corresponding PUCCH resources can be provided by multi-CSI-PUCCHResourceList.
